# Load Testing

## ApacheBench

```bash
ab -n 100000 -c 1000 http://<EC2-PUBLIC-IP>:3000/
```

Parameters:

* 100,000 Requests
* 1,000 Concurrent Users

Purpose:

* Measure throughput
* Evaluate concurrency handling
* Observe connection resets

---

## wrk

```bash
wrk -t8 -c5000 -d120s http://<EC2-PUBLIC-IP>:3000/
```

Parameters:

* 8 Threads
* 5,000 Connections
* 120 Seconds

Purpose:

* Simulate production-level traffic
* Stress test the application
* Identify performance bottlenecks

